Types

History = object
  symbol*: string
  interval*: Interval
  data*: seq[HistoryRecord]
HistoryRecord = object
  time*: int64
  open*: float64
  low*: float64
  high*: float64
  close*: float64
  volume*: int64
Interval = enum
  Int1m = "1m", Int5m = "5m", Int15m = "15m", Int30m = "30m", Int1h = "1h",
  Int1d = "1d", Int1wk = "1wk", Int1mo = "1mo"
